Class ConfigRevision

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.db.structs.ConfigRevision

  • @Entity
public class ConfigRevision
extends java.lang.Object
    For keeping track of information having to do with a configuration revision. This way can keep track of reason for processing config, when it was run, etc.
    Author:
    Michael Smith (michael@transitime.org)
